# Akka, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Akka (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Khuchninsky Selsoviet, Tabasaransky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 2 streets.
Geography
Akka is located  southwest of Khuchni (the district's administrative centre) by road. Tsurtil is the nearest rural locality.
